# feat(store): Implement full Store UI/UX вЂ” Cart, Checkout & Navigation

## Summary

This PR transforms the `StorePage` component from a bare placeholder into a fully functional, production-ready store interface for the ACSES-SRID Official Swag shop. It introduces a complete UI overhaul, a Cart page, a Checkout modal with form validation, and an order success flow.

