## What Changed

### рџ”ґ Before (Default Placeholder)
```jsx
const StorePage = () => {
  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 pt-24 pb-16">
      <div className="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <h1 className="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-acses-green-600 mb-4">
          ACSES Store
        </h1>
        <p className="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl">
          Official ACSES merchandise. Product listings and ordering coming soon.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};
```

The original implementation was a static, non-functional placeholder with no data, no components, no interactivity, and no layout structure.

---

### вњ… After (Full Implementation)

The page is now broken into modular, reusable components with full interactivity and state management.

---

## Components Added / Modified

### `<Navbar />`
- Fixed top navigation bar with increased height (`84px`) for better visual weight
- Custom inline SVG ACSES logo with green accent ring and department emblem
- Brand name **ACSES-SRID** with subtitle: *Association of Computer Science and Engineering Students вЂ“ SRID*
- Nav links: **Home**, **About**
- Shopping cart icon button with a live **red badge counter** reflecting total items in cart
- Clicking the cart icon navigates to the Cart page

---

### `<Hero />`
- Full-width dark green gradient banner (`#14532d в†’ #15803d`)
- Bold **"Official Swag"** headline
- Tagline: *"Rep your department with pride. High-quality apparel and accessories for the future tech leaders."*
- Decorative translucent circle overlays for depth

---

### `<FiltersCard />`
- Sidebar filter panel with:
  - **Category radio filters**: All Products, Apparel, Accessories, Tech Gear
  - **Sort By** dropdown: Featured, Price: Low to High, Price: High to Low, Newest
  - **"Need to pay dues?"** banner with a portal CTA button
- Sticky positioning while scrolling

---

### `<ProductCard />`
- Product image area with **BESTSELLER** (amber) and **SALE** (red) badge overlays
- Product name, description, and price in ACSES green (`#15803d`)
- Strikethrough original price displayed for sale items
- **Add to Cart** button with shopping cart icon
- Adding the same product increments quantity rather than duplicating the entry

---

### `<CartPage />` *(New)*
- Dedicated cart page (client-side navigation, no routing library required)
- Lists all cart items with:
  - Product image thumbnail
  - Name and description
  - **Quantity controls** (increment / decrement / removes at 0)
  - **Remove** button per item (red trash icon)
  - Line total per item
- Sticky **Order Summary** panel on the right:
  - Per-item breakdown
  - Subtotal
  - Delivery: **Free**
  - Grand total in green
  - **Checkout** button в†’ opens `<CheckoutModal />`
  - **Continue Shopping** button в†’ returns to store
- **Empty cart state** with icon, message, and a Browse Store button

---

### `<CheckoutModal />` *(New)*
- Scrollable modal overlay with blur backdrop
- Sticky modal header with title and close (Г—) button
- **Mini order summary** at the top of the form
- Form fields with inline validation:

  | Field | Validation |
  |---|---|
  | Full Name | Required |
  | Student ID | Required |
  | Email Address | Required, valid format |
  | Phone Number | Required |
  | Level | Required (dropdown: 100вЂ“400, Postgrad) |
  | Hall / Hostel | Optional |
  | MoMo Number | Required when Mobile Money selected |

- **Payment method toggle**: Mobile Money / Cash on Delivery
  - MoMo number input appears conditionally
- **Place Order** button shows total amount and triggers validation before submission
- On success в†’ clears cart, closes modal, shows `<SuccessModal />`

---

### `<SuccessModal />` *(New)*
- Full-screen overlay with blur backdrop
- Green `<CheckCircle />` icon
- Personalised confirmation message with customer name
- **Continue Shopping** button в†’ closes modal, clears cart, returns to store

---

## State Management

All state is managed locally in `<StorePage />` (the root component) and passed down via props:

| State | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `page` | `"store" \| "cart"` | Controls which page is rendered |
| `selectedCategory` | `string` | Active category filter |
| `sortBy` | `string` | Active sort option |
| `cartItems` | `array` | Cart entries with `id`, `qty`, `cartId` |
| `showCheckout` | `boolean` | Controls checkout modal visibility |
| `showSuccess` | `boolean` | Controls success modal visibility |
| `customerName` | `string` | Stores name from submitted checkout form |

---

